quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,28,aur jab tum aur tumahray saathi kashti mein baith jao to ( khuda ka shukar karna aur ) kehna ke sab tareef khuda hi ko ( sazawar ) hai. jis ne hum ko nijaat bakhsh zalim logon se
  23,29,aur ( yeh bhi ) dua karna ke ae perwar-digaar hum ko mubarak jagah اتاریو aur to sab se behtar aُtarne wala hai
  23,30,be shak is ( qissay ) mein nishanain hain aur hamein to azmaish karni thi
  23,31,phir un ke baad hum ne aik aur jamaat peda ki
  23,32,"aur un hi mein se un mein aik paighambar bheja ( jis ne un se kaha ) ke khuda hi ki ibadat karo ( ke ) is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi, tokiya tum drtay nahi"
  23,33,"to un ki qoum ke sardar jo kafir they aur akhirat ke anay ko jhoot samajte they aur duniya ki zindagi mein hum ne un ko aasoudgi day rakhi thi. kehnay lagey ke yeh to tum hi jaissa aadmi hai, jis qisam ka khana tum khatay ho, isi terhan ka yeh bhi khata hai aur jo pani tum peetay ho isi qisam ka yeh bhi peeta hai"
  23,34,aur agar tum apne hi jaisay aadmi ka kaha maan liya to ghatay mein par gay
  23,35,kiya yeh tum se yeh kehta hai ke jab tum mar jao ge aur matti ho jao ge aur istikhwan ( ke siwa kuch nah rahay ga ) to tum ( zameen se ) nikalay jao ge
  23,36,jis baat ka tum se wadakiya jata hai ( bohat ) baeed aur ( bohat ) baeed hai
  23,37,"zindagi to yahi hamari duniya ki zindagi hai ke ( isi mein ) hum martay aur jeetay hain, aur hum phir nahi uthaiye jayen ge"
  23,38,yeh to aik aisa aadmi hai jis ne khuda par jhoot iftirakiya hai aur hum is ko maan-ne walay nahi
  23,39,paighambar ne kaha ke ae perwar-digaar unhon ne mujhe jhoota samgha hai to meri madad kar
  23,40,farmaya ke yeh thoray hi arsay mein pasheman ho kar reh jayen ge
  23,41,"to un ko ( wadahbarhaq ke mutabiq ) zor ki aawaz ne aapkrha, to hum ne un ko kora kar daala. pas zalim logon par laanat hai"
  23,42,phir un ke baad hum ne aur jamaten peda kee
